'''''Debbie''''', ni Sinema yo muri [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afrika]] yepfo yasohotse muri 1965 iyobowe na Elmo De Witt kandi yakozwe na Jamie Uys kuri Jamie Uys Filmproduksies<ref>https://sevencircumstances.com/2019/01/12/the-private-freaky-sensuality-of-childhood-tweespoor-double-track-by-helena-gunter/debbie-1965-afrikaans-film-directed-by-elmo-de-witt/</ref>.  Muri iyi filime hagaragaramo Suzanne van Oudtshoorn mu mwanya wa mbere hamwe na Leon le Roux, Gert van den Bergh na Dawid van der Walt mu nshingano zabo.<ref>https://letterboxd.com/film/debbie/</ref><ref>https://mubi.com/films/debbie</ref>  

Filime irazenguruka umukobwa wumwangavu Debbie Malan wagiye mumujyi agasama atashyingiranywe.  Filime yakiriwe neza kandi yegukana ibihembo byinshi mubirori mpuzamahanga bya firime.<ref>https://moviefit.me/persons/242188-elmo-de-witt</ref><ref>http://www.mimosafilms.co.za/Archive/Film/69/debbie</ref>

